{"tid":457711,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2017日本代表及日本職業聯賽繼續討論73 我川繼續童貞","createTime":"2017-11-04T06:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-04T06:45:23.000Z","uid":13132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"45768d0a0fa619d9d63e660f12ccbe10cfa0d6b8","tid":457711,"uid":13132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"網上買飛方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/first\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fguide%2Ffirst&d=R%2F%2BmfF0kYNTsCQBSFggLucmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=5da326f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/first</a><br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\nlogin in 無A/C就申請A/C<br />\n申請方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/registration#reg02\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fguide%2Fregistration%23reg02&d=R%2F%2BmfF0kYNTsCQBSFggLucmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e33b0438\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/guide/registration#reg02</a><br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n揀聯賽/球隊/場次<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/01.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F01.png&h=9b9c55c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F02.png&h=15135227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n揀位<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F03.jpg&h=a4245aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四<br />\n比錢,領取方法<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F04.jpg&h=aee153be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.信用卡比錢去7仔拎<br />\n2.信用卡去OK同有サンクス、ぴあ便利店拎<br />\n3.信用卡去郵政局拎<br />\n4.去7仔比錢拎<br />\n5.去郵局/銀行比錢之後去OK同有サンクス、ぴあ便利店拎<br />\n6.去郵局/銀行比錢再郵寄<br />\n7.去OK同有サンクス、ぴあ便利店比錢之後拎<br />\n(之後用1,2,7買嘅爸打就去自己所揀嘅便利店襟返個堆數目字就搞掂)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四<br />\n買完<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.jleague-ticket.jp/img/guide/first/05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague-ticket.jp%2Fimg%2Fguide%2Ffirst%2F05.jpg&h=624b5320&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFrom 日本手足今野秦幸<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HZSwHv_4EAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHZSwHv_4EAo&d=R%2F%2BmfF0kYNTsCQBSFggLucmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c9a0f33d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HZSwHv_4EAo</a><br />\n樓豬之歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}